high_descs: Turn right and walk to the wall, then turn right and walk to the black table in the corner.
Pick up the spoon on the table.
Look at the table.
Place the spoon in the mug on the table.
Pick up the mug.
Turn around and walk to the table.
Place the mug on the table in front of the red apple.
anns.task_desc: Place a mug with a spoon in it on a table.

high_descs: Turn around and cross the room to the left to face the small black table.
Pick up the spoon on the small black table.
Look up to face the cup on the small black table.
Place the spoon in the cup.
Pick up the cup on the small black table.
Turn around and walk forward to face the kitchen table.
Place the cup on the kitchen table.
anns.task_desc: TO put a spoon in a cup plus place them on the kitchen table.

high_descs: Move towards the white door, then turn right and move to the small black table in the corner of the room to the left of the white table.
Pick up the spoon in front of the loaf of bread from the table.
Move closer to the black table.
Place the spoon in the white mug to the right of the loaf of bread on the table.
Pick up the mug containing the spoon from the table.
Turn around, move past the door, and move to the gray round table in the corner of the room.
Place the white mug containing a spoon between the edge of the table and the red apple on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a mug containing a spoon on the table.
